//
// AttestationService is the control-plane side of TPM host admission.
// Pure-Go verifier (no TPM on the control plane) ; the node side needs
// a TPM (see the node client stub). All four RPCs are UNAUTHENTICATED
// at the OIDC layer by design — the cryptographic proof IS the
// authentication. They are no-ops for trust unless the operator has
// enabled attestation AND pre-trusted the node's EK (provisioning).
